📖 Application portfolio check: 9:30 to 12:00, 13:30 to 16:30

WEDNESDAY, May 15th, 2024
👩‍🎓 Advice for an academic career: 9:30 to 12:00
📖 Application portfolio check: 9:30 to 12:00, 13:30 to 16:30

Find all information, further offers, and the career fair catalogue on https://www.konaktiva.tu-darmstadt.de/
